<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/635978-i-found-myself-toggling-to-google-maps-and">I found myself toggling to Google Maps and mapping her route from one destination to the next, viewing distances, routes, cities, and buildings. What I wished I had was her exact location in each destination. Would Ms. Park consider providing the exact coordinates of the destinations in her journey wherever she might be able to identify them? It would make a fascinating map to zoom down into and explore.</a>
</div>
